{"tid":548170,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《死神》真人電影露琪亞定妝照曝光  造型大改引熱議","createTime":"2018-02-02T08:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T14:34:27.000Z","uid":49391,"like":7,"dislike":163,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"8a4445e604ef117df12362dab7aa9f62af267dca","tid":548170,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"《死神》真人電影已經開拍了很久，官方公開消息的速度可以說讓很多人都已經快要忘記還有這部電影，昨天（2月1日）官方終於公開了朽木露琪亞的演員和她的定妝照。知名演員杉咲花將出演朽木露琪亞，官方公開的這張定妝照中的露琪亞的造型和原作還是有比較大的出入的，不過杉咲花演技還是相當給力的，期待她在電影中的表現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/02/20180202_lr_176_2/gamersky_01small_02_201822127E0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F02%2F20180202_lr_176_2%2Fgamersky_01small_02_201822127E0F.jpg&h=9ae16bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/02/20180202_lr_176_2/gamersky_02small_04_20182210036D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F02%2F20180202_lr_176_2%2Fgamersky_02small_04_20182210036D.jpg&h=c6bc052d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有關《死神》真人電影的消息，官方放出的一直比較少，從公開拍攝電影到現在只放出了男主角黑崎一護和朽木露琪亞的兩張定妝照。不過之前官方宣布《死神》真人電影將於2018年夏季上映，估計之後消息公開的速度就會加快了吧，現在真的很想知道井上織姬會由誰來出演。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/02/20180202_lr_176_2/gamersky_03small_06_20182210081F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F02%2F20180202_lr_176_2%2Fgamersky_03small_06_20182210081F.jpg&h=9fdb4c37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0106c0424f7eca86ed58fb66170ab3b91a786173","tid":548170,"uid":45613,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:00:39.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46970ccac882f07ef1b72d67f878cf376684586c","tid":548170,"uid":103380,"like":262,"dislike":1,"score":261,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"唉屌 啲片商好心唔好再拍真人